# Rule: fcop-routing

Files in `docs/agents/status/` are **routing tokens**. The **filename** encodes the next consumer; the **body** is the payload.

## Conventions

- Use descriptive slugs: `concept-to-narrative-director.md` → after processing rename to `approved-to-world-architect.md` (example pattern).
- One writer at a time per logical document; collisions **escalate** to Producer for human merge.
- Do not store secrets in queue files.

